{
  "stem": "24268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very-- I think, considered us [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I tried to be active, and as much as I draw things, and so forth, and participate in the choir.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I also-- that was our-- I would-- that was I-- childhood, I used to go with friends, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had wonderful time spending.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And matter of fact, somebody remind me, when I was in Israel, of somebody whom-- our neighbors, accidentally which I met in Israel-- she remind me how wonderful it was to visit, how much they loved to come to our backyard, to the garden.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and she asked me if I still have this beautiful voice, like a nightingale.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I say, no, it's gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's what I wanted to mention, shabbat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Friday night, there was tradition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Daddy always wear this little hat, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every day, he wore the hat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he did not shave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But on the Friday night, he just put on a certain special coat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was with a sash, a purple-- a maroon sash.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had always somebody to come, unfortunate-- the less fortunate people to be invited to-- for supper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the holidays-- matter of fact, a year before the war started, we had people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We brought a cantor from Pils.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was a cantor and the son.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were guests in our home for the high holy days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "For Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kippur, they brought in special people to pray, with good voices, and with better knowledge-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My parents, they were like-- Daddy was-- he was like a modern orthodox.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was to God and to people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And mom was, as well, and very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she helped others, as well-- needy, hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
